<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Holly Willoughby has offered a glimpse of her stunning outdoor swimming pool at her £3million five-bedroom London mansion. </p>

<p>The This Morning host, 39, had the outdoor pool built in 2013 at the home she shares with her husband Dan Baldwin, 45, and children, Belle, Harry and Chester. </p>

<p>The TV host posed with her ragdoll cat Bluebell for the Marks and Spencer shoot with the help of her children and offered a sneak peak of her pool on Thursday. </p>

<p>Wow: Holly Willoughby has offered a glimpse of her stunning outdoor swimming pool at her £3million five-bedroom London mansion</p>

<p>Holly looked radiant as she held Bluebell for the autumnal fashion shoot with her turquoise pool visible behind a wrought iron gate as she stood on the marble tiles.  </p>

<p>The beauty opted for a geo-print mustard skirt paired with a black oversized aviator jacket and black patent boots in the shot surrounded by plants trailing up the brick wall. </p>

<p>A fresh-faced Holly swept her signature blonde locks into a side parting and added a slick of pink gloss for the snap. </p>

<p>Beauty: Holly posed with a geometric print midi dress and draped a beige trench coat over her shoulders</p>

<p>Family: The star offered a glimpse of her patio dining seating, surrounded by manicured borders as her daughter Belle nailed the perfect snap</p>

<p>Close: Holly revealed on her Instagram she had recruited her eldest children Harry, 11, and nine-year-old Belle to transform her home into a fashion shoot location for the brand</p>

<p>In a second shot Holly posed with a geometric print midi dress and draped a beige trench coat over her shoulders as her daughter Belle nailed the perfect snap. </p>

<p>The star offered a glimpse of her patio dining seating, surrounded by manicured borders, decked with fairy lights and complete with a chandelier above the stone table.  </p>

<p>Holly revealed on her Instagram she had recruited her eldest children Harry, 11, and nine-year-old Belle to transform her home into a fashion shoot location for the brand.</p>

<p>Autumn: The TV star also looked a ray of sunshine despite a downpour as she posed in the rain in a stunning chunky turmeric knit paired with a navy printed shirt dress</p>

<p>Captioning a snap, she penned: 'So here it is...After giving you a sneak peek, I'm delighted to reveal the first of my favourite looks from Marks and Spencer's Autumn collection, expertly shot by my Belle whilst in quarantine ... Such classic coat and perfect with this beautiful dress... hope you like it!' </p>

<p>The TV star also looked a ray of sunshine despite a downpour as she posed in the rain in a stunning chunky turmeric knit paired with a navy printed shirt dress. </p>

<p>Holly leaned against a raised bed in her garden which boasted an array of vegetable plants including tomatoes. </p>

<p>Fun: Holly photographed her children building an ant house in garden made from twigs and stones</p>

<p>Roast: The kitchen comes complete with a marble island perfect for cooking dinner, a huge oven and sleek dove grey cabinets</p>

<p>She wrote: 'Autumn is here and the garden vegetable patch is looking a little unruly! The tomatoes (except for one) never went red. </p>

<p>'Luckily Autumn fashion is a little more reliable and a floral dress with boots is my go-to from September onwards. Keeping the sunshine with this turmeric yellow cardi for those chilly evenings... New autumn collection out now... Photography by my Harry during lockdown.</p>

<p>Holly's choice of a more neutral and modern interior inside the Edwardian house provided a calming space for her brood during lockdown.</p>

<p>Gardening: The blonde beauty previously uploaded a photo of Belle watering some seedlings</p>

<p>Flower fancy: Featured in a number of Holly's shots is stunning flowers, scattered around her home, including plush orchids and intricate bouquets to add flourish to the home</p>

<p>A glimpse into her home shows the kitchen complete with a marble island perfect for cooking dinner, a huge oven and sleek dove grey cabinets.  </p>

<p>And if Holly wants a bit of rest and relaxation she can retreat to her luxurious free-standing bath in the bathroom- if her cat Bluebell doesn't get there first.   </p>

<p>Holly's garden comes complete with a rolling lawn, playhouse and plant pots, where the children can grown their own vegetables. </p>

<p>Cute: Bluebell certainly has plenty of space to roam, with Holly uploading snaps of her feline friend's activities</p>

<p>Keeping the kids entertained: Holly's background where she usually poses for photos was used by Harry as an impromptu spot for football training with a 50p coin</p>

<p>The blonde beauty previously uploaded a photo of Belle watering some seedlings.   </p>

<p>Holly's love for Emma Bridgewater's work is predominant, with a number of snaps showing her home littered with the work - which includes mugs costing £56. </p>

<p>Showing her love for Emma's work, she shared a snap of her Christmas collection while adding the caption: 'Very excited in the <?php echo e('@'); ?>thismorning prep kitchen as the <?php echo e('@'); ?>emma_bridgewater Christmas collection arrives'.</p>

<p>Peek-a-boo! If Holly wants a bit of rest and relaxation from home schooling, she can retreat her luxurious free-standing bath in the bathroom- if her cat Bluebell doesn't get there first</p>

<p>Sundays in her home are a consistent theme on Holly's account, as she was seen to post a chicken ready for the oven while adding the caption: 'Sunday bliss... Cooking a roast, listening to Bowie's Hunky Dory album'. </p>

<p>In her choice of decorations, Holly's home features a vast custom-made neon light featuring a dagger pierced through a heart with the words 'H&amp;D Forever' on top.   </p>

<p>Featured in a number of Holly's shots is stunning flowers, scattered around her home, including plush orchids and intricate bouquets to add flourish. </p>

<p>True love: Holly shares the five-bedroom Edwardian house with her husband Dan Baldwin, whom she married in 2007</p>
